text: :Another Enamul Haque also played for Bangladesh Enamul Haque (born 5 December 1986 in Sylhet), is a Bangladeshi cricketer. He is known as Enamul Haque jr because a Bangladeshi player Enamul Haque played before him. He is a right- handed batsman. He bowls a slow left-arm delivery. ==References== Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Bangladeshi cricketers Category:Bangladeshi Muslims Category:People from Sylhet Division
